additional_house_rules:
We’re pretty chill & laid back, however, there are just a few rules & things you need to be aware of in order to keep the good vibes alive.

• The space is quiet and it is hard to hear neighbors, but late night/early morning partying is frowned upon. There is a $25/person guest fee for anyone in the unit in addition to the amount booked.


• No matter how fabulous your shoes are, please remove them while inside the unit.


• Check in is at 3:00pm and check out is at 11:00am. An early check in of 1:00pm and a late check out of 1:00pm MAY be available for $50 each. Anything before a 1:00pm check in or after a 1:00pm check out will be a half day rate. Please let us know your arrival and departure times beforehand.


• There is an additional person fee of $40/per guest per evening after 1 guest. Please include the correct number of guests in your booking request so that I may provide the appropriate amount of amenities.


• We wouldn't are ask you to leave your furry friends at home! There is an additional $125 pet fee for the entirety of your stay. Let me know ahead of time and I will provide water, food bowls or even litter boxes!


• We love kids too! High chairs, pack and plays, and booster seats can be rented for $50 each per stay.


• Air mattresses can be provided complimentary upon request, lux air mattresses may be available for rent for $60 each per stay.


• Our space is non-smoking and no smoking is allowed in the unit. You are welcome to smoke outside. There will be a $500 fine for smoking inside the unit.


• Let me know if you have any questions, concerns or needs for your stay. We are here to make sure your trip is superb! Make yourself at home and enjoy! #BANGTELLOVESYOU
description:
Wake up in the city that doesn't sleep! This 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom is so chic, Carrie Bradshaw would be jealous. Strut the streets to the upscale shops of Fifth avenue, or sing your way to a show on Broadway. Complete with in unit washer-dryer, this Midtown spot will let you live it up in luxury.

• Looking to host an event, birthday or a party for the sake of partying? 
Rates starting at $500 plus additional person fee.

• Need a space to shoot your next print ad or film the next box office hit? 
Photo shoots starting at $1000/day and productions starting at $1500/day.

INQUIRE WITHIN!

I am just a call or text away if you need anything!
